{
  "stem": "7093.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, when the Germans came, then I was there in this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for the next four weeks, I spent practically in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, except the three days after the-- after the occupation, I was in hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was operated with a perforated colon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very, very ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then four days afterwards-- this was in the Jewish hospital in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And four days afterwards, the Germans threw out all the Jews from the hospital and took over the hospital, so that four days after this heavy operation, I was thrown out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With the saying-- with the advice that I must keep a diet from then on my whole life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am afraid-- I mean, I'm afraid later on, I did keep a diet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't have anything to eat, so I kept a very good diet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I-- and, and I wasn't-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wasn't supposed to carry anything heavy, which I, unfortunately, I couldn't also keep to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I will talk about that consequently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- my parents wanted me to come home after the-- when I came out from hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And but we couldn't travel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had to have special permission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had to wait.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I, I asked for permission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I first had to make up my mind whether I really wanted to go home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had two offers of being hidden by, by non-Jews, of being hidden and also-- and being provided with false papers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I had a choice whether I go back or I was going to-- or I risk it, risk living with false papers and in hiding.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I decided to go back because at my last visit, I had a very big row with my father, and I wanted to make up with him.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
